www-subtext: Ukufikelela kwiimpendulo ezivulelekileyo ezisi-1.2 sezigidi ngokusebenzisa le dashbhodi isebenzisanayo, isixhobo esisodwa esidibanisa amazwi abasetyhini kunye namantombazana kunye namathuba angenasiphelo ohlalutyo lwedijithali.

pmnch-subtext: Wamkelekile kwiDashboard ethi "Into Efunwa Lulutsha"! Esi sixhobo sokusebenzisana sinika ukubonakaliswa okubonakalayo kweempendulo kunye nokuqonda esikuhlanganisayo kubantu abatsha abaneminyaka eyi-10-24 emhlabeni jikelele. Ingundoqo yeli nyathelo ngumbuzo ovulekileyo: "Ukuphucula impilo yam, ndifuna ...". Abantu abatsha abavela kwihlabathi liphela bebephendula oku, besinika iimbono ezizodwa ngeemfuno zabo, amathemba, kunye nolangazelelo lwabo. Jonga idatha, fumana amabali ngasemva kwamanani, kwaye uhlanganyele nathi ekwandiseni amazwi abantu abancinci be-1.8 yezigidigidi kwihlabathi liphela. Ukufunda ngakumbi ngeli phulo, ndwendwela http://www.1point8.org.
